{"tid":1362811,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一批公務員促特首回應訴求　不排除籌備按章工作或罷工","createTime":"2019-07-25T03:33:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T10:17:19.000Z","uid":40152,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d96dc8af34c23b88c6f940fc7823882bffa11755","tid":1362811,"uid":40152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T03:33:07.000Z","msg":"一批公務員促特首回應訴求　不排除籌備按章工作或罷工<br />\n<br />\n來自44個政策局和部門的200多名公務員向行政長官林鄭月娥發公開信，強烈要求政府回應民間五大訴求，如果政府繼續漠視民意，他們將會籌備具體工業行動。<br />\n<br />\n公開信批評，過去兩個月，港人參與了一連串反修例遊行，表達訴求，但政府一直依然故我，拒絕聆聽大眾的聲音，違背服務市民的承諾；星期日元朗的襲擊事件，更令人對警方執法能力存疑，有負市民期望，亦令公務員質疑政府機構並非為民服務，更令公務員成為社會撕裂的幫兇。<br />\n<br />\n公開信表示，身為公僕理應適切回應人民訴求，因此決定打破沉默，強烈要求政府直接面對民意。<br />\n<br />\n有份聯署公開信、來自創新及科技局的陳先生，接受本台查詢時表示，工業行動包括按章工作，亦有同事希望籌組跨部門罷工行動。他說，不會為政府的回應定下死線，但相信當局在8月中之前會有交代。<br />\n<br />\n陳先生認為，公務員罷工在香港歷史上而言，會對政府造成很大挫敗，過去特首的想法是依賴公務員和警察作為支援後盾，今次行動是要表態，公務員不贊同當局過去一段長時間以來的管治手法。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1470356-20190725.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1470356-20190725.htm&d=%2FPdnyacYoUlJSF57jd07D3s01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=10191cb8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1470356-20190725.htm&h=26337fab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1470356-20190725.htm</a>"},{"pid":"0a202450f7018dce8a6ab6d6739f3221b4ffa9b3","tid":1362811,"uid":226103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T03:36:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fbd1d5bb0ea98df53e8e43e765da4e1f482d14c5","tid":1362811,"uid":57710,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T03:43:41.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"96ecf94ab5a2bc0a361b8082eb3990a295d86cd4","tid":1362811,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T03:50:04.000Z","msg":"大律師公會前主席石永泰促請政府成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1362836\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1362836</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4e29ded739a24b1af53d352d2ed59c8b70acc8ac","tid":1362811,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T03:53:14.000Z","msg":"永久罷工 ! 直至光復香港 !"},{"pid":"2ab0b8cf5926522a764c03b5be6739148c0c7ade","tid":1362811,"uid":207087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T03:58:38.000Z","msg":"有人性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21fc8eed8cf07e4907f1d0bed506b0f4ad936301","tid":1362811,"uid":220438,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T04:05:39.000Z","msg":"你班公墓猿本來就hea做 按乜撚章工作呀 人唔笑狗都吠"},{"pid":"e1d9d65d26e7935dd2c55550f8943734f6b1ecd5","tid":1362811,"uid":288492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T04:10:18.000Z","msg":"集體辭職，直至光復香港 !"},{"pid":"16f4444bff72870eb545484634c99848ade5b461","tid":1362811,"uid":103325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T04:14:30.000Z","msg":"搞到連紀律部隊同公務員都要企出嚟反對林鄭<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"558fb6e4bb65e6b7c1667122e7da0daa78ac1726","tid":1362811,"uid":18104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T04:21:56.000Z","msg":"以我理解公墓員一向都係按章工作<br />\n仲可以點樣加按？"},{"pid":"2d806aaadd3aa3b65ad0fb8a03d0de7006c02f0f","tid":1362811,"uid":126305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:05:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"302c28a95390ad4e4e320e449e80c8e70425898a","tid":1362811,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"558fb6e4bb65e6b7c1667122e7da0daa78ac1726","tid":1362811,"uid":18104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T04:21:56.000Z","msg":"以我理解公墓員一向都係按章工作<br />\n仲可以點樣加按？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:06:58.000Z","msg":"唔好咁講<br />\n稅局 同 運輸處 如果按章工作真係仆街<br />\n<br />\n你有上過去搞稅同續車牌就知"},{"pid